{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_plosis_set_1", "eventName": "深暗之夢", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "深暗之夢", "storyInfo": "無機質的聲音，冷淡的表情，掩蓋了白面鴞內心不為人知的秘密。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  所有這些資訊都與我們的假設吻合。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  現在我們有了資料，萊茵生命的最新研究成果能和古老薩卡茲傳說直接對應，我不覺得這是巧合。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  而如果我們的假設得到證實，就會更新我們對源石的大多數已有認識。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  人們認為源石是能量，是災害；人們認為它可以被用作武器，覺得它可以得到限制性的應用，但實際情況可能不只如此。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  如果源石真的是“儲存了資訊”，那你想像一下，我們可以從源石裡解讀出這片大地的故事，百年前，千年前，甚至更久以前......", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你真的不好奇這一切嗎？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我同意你的猜想，你之前寫的報告我都看過了。", "name": "喬伊絲"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  但是我要怎麼幫你呢？", "name": "喬伊絲"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你答應了？太好了......謝謝你。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我有一個很大膽的計畫......", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_rhodesroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  6月18日 天氣晴", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  今天在食堂睡著了，被古米小姐擔心了。", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  赫默醫生提醒我，這個月我的“嗜睡症”變嚴重了。", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我的體檢報告裡有更詳細的內容。", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  “長期的睡眠品質問題導致的精神疲倦”，這是體檢的結語。", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  赫默醫生說，這是我大腦裡的晶片——九號裝置導致的。", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這些情況我都瞭解，我比擔心我的人更清楚自己的問題所在，但我仍然需要接收她們的關心。", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  赫默醫生建議我多休息，我也認可這種應對方式。但是休息的時候應該幹什麼呢？", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "巡林者"}, "figure_art": "char_503_rang"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  請繼續部署您的棋子。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不用了，不用了。", "name": "巡林者"}, "figure_art": "char_503_rang"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這一盤......老夫輸了。", "name": "巡林者"}, "figure_art": "char_503_rang"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_500_noirc_1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嘿，這可太少見了，老爺子你上一次輸棋是什麼時候來著?", "name": "黑角"}, "figure_art": "char_500_noirc_1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  上一次......確實有點久了。", "name": "巡林者"}, "figure_art": "char_503_rang"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#5$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  依據三個小時前的記錄節點，目前的棋局比分是二比一。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#5$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  如果按照三局兩勝的棋局計算方式，您依然贏得了棋局，巡林者先生。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_500_noirc_1"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "黑角"}, "figure_art": "char_500_noirc_1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "巡林者"}, "figure_art": "char_503_rang"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_500_noirc_1"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  噗哈哈哈哈哈哈......", "name": "黑角"}, "figure_art": "char_500_noirc_1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哈哈哈......這算是給我這個老頭子挽回一點尊嚴嗎。", "name": "巡林者"}, "figure_art": "char_503_rang"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#4$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  無法解讀您這句話的實際表意。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#4$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#4$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  小姑娘，你來找我教你下棋，而我教了你二十分鐘。", "name": "巡林者"}, "figure_art": "char_503_rang"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  接下來才下了三盤棋，僅僅三盤，老夫已經輸得心服口服。", "name": "巡林者"}, "figure_art": "char_503_rang"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這就是輸棋啊，小姑娘。", "name": "巡林者"}, "figure_art": "char_503_rang"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#8$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  明白。表意已確認。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#8$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_500_noirc_1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  說起來，為什麼突然想到要學下棋？白面鴞小姐你難得休息吧。", "name": "黑角"}, "figure_art": "char_500_noirc_1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  醫療部最近不是挺忙的？", "name": "黑角"}, "figure_art": "char_500_noirc_1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  赫默醫生的建議。赫默醫生認為我需要額外的愛好來分散注意力。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  所以就下棋嗎？", "name": "巡林者"}, "figure_art": "char_503_rang"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_500_noirc_1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你真的是第一次接觸這種棋類遊戲？你學得太快了。", "name": "黑角"}, "figure_art": "char_500_noirc_1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唉，剛才俺還想要不要和你下一盤，現在看還是算了。", "name": "黑角"}, "figure_art": "char_500_noirc_1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這種棋類遊戲是第一次接觸。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  在此之前，與其他幹員學習過不同的棋牌類遊戲。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  大部分遊戲活動的持續時間都很短。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_500_noirc_1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  俺猜到發生啥事了，大概是後來全都輸給白面鴞小姐了吧......", "name": "黑角"}, "figure_art": "char_500_noirc_1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#4$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  （點頭）", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#4$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#4$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不過也不奇怪，醫療部的幹員都是很優秀的年輕人，能在醫療源石技藝上有所造詣，學下棋對你來說確實不難。", "name": "巡林者"}, "figure_art": "char_503_rang"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  如果想下棋的話，為什麼不去找博士呢？這些棋類遊戲他基本上都會，而且水準很高。", "name": "巡林者"}, "figure_art": "char_503_rang"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_500_noirc_1"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  想找博士下棋，也得等他有時間吧......那個人恨不得把自己切成三份幹活呢。", "name": "黑角"}, "figure_art": "char_500_noirc_1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  啊，是老夫失言了。", "name": "巡林者"}, "figure_art": "char_503_rang"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  巡林者先生，是否結束今日的棋局？", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  現在幾點了？", "name": "巡林者"}, "figure_art": "char_503_rang"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_500_noirc_1"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我看看......我的錶呢?", "name": "黑角"}, "figure_art": "char_500_noirc_1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  下午四點三十五分，距離巡林者先生的工作規劃，即本日的執勤，還有三個小時整。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒事，時間還夠，可以再來一盤。", "name": "巡林者"}, "figure_art": "char_503_rang"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#5$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  但，推測巡林者先生本日可能會有額外的工作安排。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#5$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#5$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哦？", "name": "巡林者"}, "figure_art": "char_503_rang"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#4$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 