 "attributes": {"content": "  羅德島艦內人員請注意，羅德島艦內人員請注意。", "name": "廣播"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  為了規避天災，羅德島將於兩個小時後進行規避機動。", "name": "廣播"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  請艦內其他人員按照員工手冊提前進行機動準備。", "name": "廣播"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#2$1", "name2": "char_503_rang", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  哈哈哈，看起來還真是這樣，那今天這盤棋就下到這裡了，老夫去做一些工作準備。", "name": "巡林者"}, "figure_art": "char_503_rang"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_500_noirc_1"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  有時候俺很好奇啊，白面鴞小姐，你是怎麼做到......", "name": "黑角"}, "figure_art": "char_500_noirc_1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ？", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#2$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_500_noirc_1"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  算了，當俺沒問吧。這話想想有些不禮貌。", "name": "黑角"}, "figure_art": "char_500_noirc_1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_corridor", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  6月22日 天氣晴", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  今天我去找了梅爾，對九號裝置的運作情況進行了我無法獨自進行的檢查。", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  梅爾提出了一個令人擔憂的可能性，我對此有過思考，我也有自己的預期。", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  另一方面，九號裝置對我的大腦造成了很大的負擔，它的影響本身並未加大，但我的承受能力肯定不能永遠保持在當前水準。", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  戴拉是個天才。她的成果——即便有瑕疵——也必須得到保護。", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  九號裝置對我確實有負面影響，也存在故障可能。但如果不是它穩定了我先天的腦部障礙，我連發表這些評估的機會都不會有。", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  此外，戴拉的發明還為我帶來了許多機能上的提升。其中一些是我們實驗之前就有預期的，一些則效果超出了預料。", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我能夠看到源石粒子在人體內的流動，基於此，我對醫療類源石技藝的理解與掌控能力也有了驚人的強化。", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  當時，戴拉認為，這不僅是大腦算力大幅度提升的結果，還因為我透過它發掘了一部分源石作為資訊儲存載體的功能性。", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這就是九號裝置。", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  顯然，它還可以有其他用途......它可以成為武器。它能救人，它也可以造成破壞，就像源石本身一樣，但是運用起來要更加直觀。", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......這不是戴拉想要的結果。", "name": "日記"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_242_mayer#2", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  稍等下......我看看......", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer#2"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  電壓很穩定，接收器沒問題......", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer#2"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_242_mayer#4"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒什麼問題，九號裝置的運作很正常。", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer#4"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  申請讀取資料功能部分是否有變化？", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#4$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_242_mayer#3"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......嗯......", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer#3"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  很可惜，還是沒有。", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer#3"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你真的確定這九號裝置可以輸出資料？", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer#3"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這是設計師最初設計的功能。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_242_mayer#3"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  但是這麼久了，我根本沒有接收到任何有意義的資料。", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer#3"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  而且說真的，腦袋裡有這麼一塊晶片，你真的不會覺得難受？", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer#3"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  就算是電信號傳輸，我覺得多多少少對身體還是有點影響的吧，我自己遙控設備的時候就很小心的。", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer#3"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  迄今為止，沒有任何影響生理指標的副作用。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_242_mayer"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  戴拉蕾德小姐是真的很厲害......這個項目甚至沒有工程科參與，它是超越性的發明。", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_242_mayer#3"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我很好奇這東西的具體構造！有什麼辦法能讓我研究一下嗎？圖紙啊，備用零件什麼的。", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer#3"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  否定，九號裝置沒有額外的備份。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_242_mayer"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唉，太可惜了。", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  但是......喬伊絲......", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  什麼樣的機器都有自己的使用壽命。", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  九號裝置的設計過於複雜，這不只是一塊晶片的問題。", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  它連接著你的小腦，與你腦內的大量神經互相影響。", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  整個系統中的任何一個零件出現問題，都會造成災難性的結果。", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我不知道你和戴拉蕾德小姐是怎麼想的......就算按萊茵生命的標準，這也有點太冒險了。", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......生物結構......", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#5$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_242_mayer#2"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我知道你想說什麼啦。", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer#2"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_242_mayer#4"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  “生物結構的本質就是一套運作合理的精密機械”，對吧。", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer#4"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_242_mayer#2"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這話聽著像是工程科的那群老骨頭說的。", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer#2"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_242_mayer#3"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  但是你必須要面對一個現實問題。", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer#3"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  如果有一天，九號裝置出了故障，或者乾脆就失效了，你該怎麼辦？", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer#3"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#4$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_242_mayer#3"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  具體的報告我沒有看完，但是赫默說你現在甚至需要九號裝置來維持生命吧。", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer#3"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  定期的體檢是必須的。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_242_mayer"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這不是體檢的問題，這涉及你的生命安全欸！", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  明白。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#4$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_242_mayer"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  或許這句話不該我來說......但是你真的......", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你真的不考慮一下羅德島的幫助？", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  去問問可露希爾小姐？她真的是我這些年見過的最厲害的工程師之一。", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  感謝你的擔心，梅爾小姐。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  此問題會由後續的狀況評估。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_242_mayer"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......唉......", "name": "梅爾"}, "figure_art": "char_242_mayer"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又是一場深夢。"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夢中，喬伊絲站在一片迷霧之中，耳邊不斷傳來陣陣低語。"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她無法理解低語的內容，這是一種她從來沒有聽過，也不曾瞭解的語言。"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它來自很遙遠的地方，低沉得幾不可聞。"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她漫無目的地遊蕩在迷霧與夢境之中。"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠處似乎傳來了光，光芒刺破迷霧，照亮了周圍。"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她看到了一塊巨大的源石結晶，結晶裡閃耀著奇特的光芒。"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_infirmary", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_108_silent_1#4", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  嗯......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#4"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  目前來看，你的所有關鍵生理指標都是正常的。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#4"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不過你的睡眠品質還是很差，還是會有持續整晚的夢境嗎？", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#4"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是的。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_108_silent_1#4"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這是一個很不好的信號，你這種狀態持續太久了。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#4"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  生理指標沒有異常。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_108_silent_1#3"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  當前的生理指標不能說明任何問題，你自己應該也很明白。你得不到休息，長期來看，這會是致命的。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#3"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  或許我們應該去諮詢一下凱爾希醫生。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#3"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  她的話，一定有辦法緩解你的精神壓力。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#3"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  否定，九號裝置是萊茵生命的保密實驗項目。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_108_silent_1#3"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  他們說不定已經不在乎這個項目了。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#3"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  戴拉蕾德小姐的項目組也早就解散了。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#3"}, {"id": 265, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_108_silent_1#4"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你可能——你就是——整個九號裝置項目最後的遺產了。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#4"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  赫默醫生，你相信那個說法嗎？", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#4$1"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_108_silent_1#3"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你指的是什麼？", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#3"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  “源石中儲存著這片大地的資訊，可以追溯到百年，千年，甚至更久之前。”", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#4$1"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_108_silent_1#3"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  （歎氣）", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#3"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_108_silent_1#5"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  在萊茵生命的時候，我並不瞭解戴拉蕾德小姐的項目......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#5"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我無法回答你這個問題，這不是我的專業。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#5"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  但從儀器的反饋資料來判斷，我認為你在夢中看到的一切，都只是九號裝置帶來的副作用。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#5"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你可能是把一些清醒時接收的資訊進行了重構，然後在夢中反覆播放。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#5"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  “反覆播放”是九號裝置的副作用之一，類似於它給你帶來的強邏輯思考方式。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#5"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  九號裝置會強制讓你的大腦保持興奮狀態，這也是你睡眠品質差與“嗜睡症”的源頭。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#5"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......你也知道，戴拉蕾德小姐的項目實際上有很多問題，大部分基礎理論都還只停留在推測，缺乏更多的論證。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#5"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  整個實驗的基礎理論都欠缺解釋，他們強行讓戴拉蕾德小姐進行了實驗，所以你才會變成現在這樣。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#5"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  當時萊茵內部普遍認為這項實驗是失敗的，也導致你......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#5"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  否定，描述並非真實情況。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  外部判斷缺乏關鍵資訊，這不是戴拉的錯。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_108_silent_1#5"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我不是要指責戴拉蕾德......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#5"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......戴拉？你平時是這麼稱呼她的?", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#5"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  是的。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#5$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_108_silent_1#3"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#3"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我知道戴拉蕾德小姐是你的朋友。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#3"}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  戴拉蕾德的死......和你無關，我無權責怪她，但是她對於自己研究的過度執著也確實導向了悲劇。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#3"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  這樣的悲劇......我已經在萊茵生命見過太多了。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#3"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  唉，如果真的是因為戴拉蕾德小姐，你可以和我聊一聊，你也可以和梅爾聊一聊。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#3"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  不要總是對那一句話耿耿於懷。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#3"}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  也不要總是憋在心裡。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#3"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  如果你長期以來都時刻保持著這樣緊張的精神狀態，對你的身體沒有任何好處。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#3"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  你現在是我的助手，也是我的朋友。我還是希望我的朋友......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#3"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_108_silent_1#5"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......我還是希望我的朋友們能夠活得更好。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#5"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  明白了。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  讓你擔心了，赫默醫生。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  重新登記與赫默醫生的身份關係——", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#1$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ——朋友。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#3$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_108_silent_1"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  ......你都有心情開玩笑了，看起來確實問題不大。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_108_silent_1#4"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  下周還要和凱爾希醫生一起出外勤，你這樣我實在是不放心。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1#4"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_108_silent_1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  總之，如果回頭你還有什麼異常情況，一定要記得告訴我。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  謝謝你，赫默醫生。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#3$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_108_silent_1"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  對了，一會要麻煩你把這些藥送給伊芙利特。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  我今天可能得晚點回去。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "char_108_silent_1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "  沒有問題，赫默醫生。", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#7$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_room_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 329, "pr